name: superpowers-harness
version: 0.1.0
recommends: superpowers — if not auto-installed, run (claude OR copilot): plugin marketplace add obra/superpowers-marketplace && plugin install superpowers@superpowers-marketplace

# This harness ships no gates — its whole job is to enable a companion plugin
# through each host's native settings file. omakase reads this one manifest
# (identity here; gate: blocks would go below), places it, and snapshots it.
